<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ن ف ل:</span> <span class="c2">(النَّفْلُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(النَّافِلَةُ)</span> عَطِيَّةُ التَّطَوُّعِ وَمِنْهُ <span class="c2">(نَافِلَةُ)</span> الصَّلَاةِ. وَ <span class="c2">(النَّافِلَةُ)</span> أَيْضًا وَلَدُ الْوَلَدِ. وَ <span class="c2">(النَّفَلُ)</span> بِفَتْحَتَيْنِ الْغَنِيمَةُ وَالْجَمْعُ <span class="c2">(الْأَنْفَالُ)</span> .<span class="c5"> قَالَ لَبِيدٌ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِنَّ تَقْوَى رَبِّنَا خَيْرُ نَفَلْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">تَقُولُ مِنْهُ:</span> <span class="c2">(نَفَّلَهُ تَنْفِيلًا)</span> أَيْ أَعْطَاهُ نَفَلًا. وَ <span class="c2">(التَّنَفُّلُ)</span> التَّطَوُّعُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>